re, and show that they appear in areas of strong\nvorticity or electric current density.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Dec 2018 17:10:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Apr 2019 14:48:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-15"}
